Quickstrike:



Quickstrike turned around to see Transulas. "Not stealin' 'er," he said to 
him. "Ah heard her screamin', so ah came t' see what it was." Just then, 
Quickstrike took a curious sniff in the air. There was a slight familiar 
scent in the air. It was from the female mouse. He sniffed again. He had 
smelt it before. At that, he remembered being in the forest, sitting on a 
log, with his leg badly damaged. He thought she had been there, right in 
that forest. And once, he may have heard her voice over comm-link.

He had to find out. Maybe he could and save her if she was with them. She 
had to be. She was near a group of Predacons when he had his leg busted 
open. Seeing her in her present condition made him a little nervous.

He stared at her body. "Ah hear you b'fore?" Nothing at the moment could 
tear his optics way from his stare, only if they pulled him by force and hit 
him.
